00:07:15.200 --> 00:07:22.880
very highly dynamic on-and-off system. And so it's very very dynamic, you know, it's very interesting,

00:07:22.880 --> 00:07:27.840
raises a lot of questions, you know, to what we're actually seeing in our ChIP-seq and Cut&Tag and

00:07:27.840 --> 00:07:34.400
