and transcriptional aberrations

00:07:45.040 --> 00:07:51.520
are one of the key features and hallmarks, in particular in pre-leukemic stem cells, and

00:07:51.520 --> 00:07:58.000
are key mediators of the differentiation block that's pathognomonic for MDS and AML, and so,

